com.betfair.cougar.modules.zipkin.impl

Class ZipkinAnnotationsStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.betfair.cougar.modules.zipkin.impl.ZipkinAnnotationsStore

  • public final class ZipkinAnnotationsStore
extends Object
    A container used for storing Zipkin annotations relative to a specific Zipkin span, to be sent once the span has been fully populated.
